Greta Adami (amụrụ n'abalị iri atọ n'ọnwa Julaị n'afọ 1992) bụ onye Ịtali na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-agba n'etiti  nye otu egwuregwu AC Milan ma gosipụta na otu ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Ịtali.
Emeela Adami ka ọ bụrụ onye otu mba Ịtali, ma gosipụtakwa n'otu ahụ n'oge 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle.
